OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FInquiry ordered over       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fschools funding blunder    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Schools may have to redraw budgets for 
OL,6, the next academic year after the       
OL,7, Department for Education admitted it   
OL,8, miscalculated its funding plans.       
OL,10,FAlmost #370m too much was allocated to 
OL,11,Fschools in England for the 2024/25 year
OL,12,Fdue to an accounting error.            
OL,14,FWhile the money had not yet been paid  
OL,15,Fout, the leader of the head teachers'  
OL,16,Funion called the mistake "frustrating" 
OL,17,Ffor teachers planning for next year.   
OL,19,FThe government has ordered an inquiry  
OL,20,Fand the department has apologised.     
